title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - May 27 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - May 27 2022
description:
Florida Governor Ron DeSantis joins Clay to talk baseball and Memorial Day. Clay takes more calls from law-enforcement on the Texas school shooting. Clay talks to Nick Leo, who reached out to Clay to get a signed letter from President Trump for his 99-year-old WWII vet grandfather.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
